column2: Not staged (cases that have AJCC staging scheme and staging was not done)
Fourth Edition (published 1992), recommended for use for cases diagnosed 1993-1997
Fifth Edition (published 1997), recommended for use for cases diagnosed 1998-2002
Sixth Edition (published 2002), recommended for use for cases diagnosed 2003-2009
Seventh Edition (published 2009), recommended for use with cases diagnosed 2010-2017
Eighth Edition (published 2016), recommended for use with cases diagnosed 2018+ for which a later edition has not yet been released
Ninth Edition (first chapter published 2020), recommended for use with chapter-specific cases diagnosed 2021+
Not applicable (cases that do not have an AJCC staging scheme)
